sequenceDiagram
    participant U as Workspace Signal Snapshot
    participant M as Master Agent
    participant D as Signal Discovery Agent
    participant S as Pattern Scoring Agent
    participant B as Blueprint Architect Agent
    participant G as Safety Governance Agent
    participant I as Syntrix IQ Layer
    participant L as Learning Loop Agent

    U->>M: Provide synthetic work signals
    M->>D: Detect repeated workflows
    D->>S: Send workflow clusters and metrics
    S->>B: Send ranked opportunities
    I->>B: Provide cited synthetic grounding sources
    B->>G: Submit generated agent blueprint
    I->>G: Provide governance and traceability evidence
    G->>L: Return governed blueprint
    L->>M: Recommend controlled v1.1 update
    M->>U: Return reasoning trace, scores, blueprint, gates, and learning recommendation
